# Task Manager - Dependencies

## Required Software
- Java JDK 21 or higher
- Terminal / Command Line

## Required Libraries (included in libs/)
- FlatLaf: for dark theme UI
- Log4J 2: for logging
- GSON: for JSON processing

## Compilation
Use: javac -cp "libs/*" -d out src/main/java/**/*.java

## Execution
Use: java -cp "out:libs/*" ui.SwingApp
EOF

