# Changelog

## [1.0.0] - 2024-01-01
### Added
- Initial release of Task Manager application
- Complete task management functionality (CRUD)
- User authentication and registration system
- Priority system (1-5) with sorting
- Deadline tracking with overdue task detection
- Modern dark theme UI with FlatLaf
- File-based local storage
- Comprehensive logging with Log4J
